title: This movie is perfect
review: Just when you thought it doesnt get any better than IT chapter one... you are most definitely wrong. This movie is perfection at its finest. The scenes, the sounds, the dialogue, are just unbelievably amazing. Wouldve gave this movie a 69 on 10 if i could.
